  "id": "019d286c-c8e3-7462-a4e5-a22b0accba94",
  "content": "div style=\"padding-left: 156px; font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n      Graph expansion: 30 vector seeds &rarr; 1,104 neighbors across 11,756 edges. Each neighbor = point lookup + 768-dim cosine.\n    </div>\n    <!-- Augmentation — zero -->\n    <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;\">\n      <div style=\"width: 140px; text-align: right; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent-green); flex-shrink: 0;\">Augmentation</div>\n      <div style=\"flex: 1; height: 40px; background: var(--bg-card); border-radius: 8px; position: relative; border: 1px solid var(--border);\">\n        <div style=\"position: absolute; left: 98%; top: 0; height: 100%; width: 1%; background: rgba(16,185,129,0.6); border-radius: 6px;\"></div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"width: 70px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent-green); flex-shrink: 0;\">&lt;1ms</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- The punchline -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;\">\n    <div class=\"stat-box\" style=\"flex: 1; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-blue);\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 44px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent-blue);\">9%</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">of time is<br>embedding inference</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"stat-box\" style=\"flex: 1; border-top: 4px solid var(--accent-amber);\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 44px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--accent-amber);\">89%</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">of time is<br>search + graph</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"stat-box\" style=\"flex: 1; border-top: 4px solid var(--text-muted);\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 44px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--text-muted);\">2%</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">of time is<br>HTTP overhead</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <p>The embedding backend everyone benchmarks? It's less than 10% of the real-world latency. In a RAG pipeline, the retrieval layer — not the model — is what your users actually wait for.</p>\n  </div>",
